to launch any application: ctrl+space
to access passwords: alt+space
to switch workspaces: win+<num> (Where <num> is a number that corresponds to the workspace you want to use.)

quick help

access terminal: win+enter run commands by typing a name and pressing enter
access firefox: win+m
make windows fullscreen: win+t
make windows tile: win+e
shut down: shift+f12
switch between window: either mouse over or use win+j/win+k
make small window take half the screen: win+space

to take notes open leafpad
email is either thunderbird or terminal and run m. If you run mail from the terminal you'll be asked for a password, it's my login. Select a message with j/k, open with enter.
